    "population": "Patients receiving anesthesia services across preanesthesia, intraoperative, and postanesthesia phases.",
    "clinical_setting": "Anesthesia care continuum and anesthesia medical records.",
    "applicability_note": "Exact for documentation fields and continuity of anesthesia records. It supports recording clinician-assessed facts and completed plans, not generating management, medicines, doses, procedures, referrals, discharge, or urgency.",
    "recency_verification": {
      "verified_on": "2026-07-13",
